data.description: Welcome to the Official Page of Apostle Joshua Selman Who is the Founder of Koinonia (Eternity Network International) , Zaria , Kaduna State , Nigeria.  KOINONIA is a weekly programme organised by the Eternity Network International where people come to experience WORSHIP, WORD, MIRACLES AND LOVE, experience true intimacy with the Holy spirit and learn to be with Him, be like Him and represent Him  Intimacy, partnership, fellowship, intercourse, and participation with the Holy spirit…we represent the fullness of God’s life on earth.
